# Alembic Migrations for Aelus-Aether

This directory contains database migrations managed by Alembic.

## Usage

### Create a new migration
```bash
alembic revision -m "description of changes"
# or with autogenerate (requires models)
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "description"
```

### Apply migrations
```bash
# Upgrade to latest
alembic upgrade head

# Upgrade one version
alembic upgrade +1

# Downgrade one version
alembic downgrade -1
```

### View migration history
```bash
alembic history
alembic current
```

## Environment Variables

Set `DATABASE_URL` environment variable to override the default database connection:
```bash
export DATABASE_URL="postgresql+asyncpg://user:pass@localhost:5432/dbname"
```

## Migration Files

Migration files are stored in `migrations/versions/` and are automatically
named with a revision ID and the message you provide.
